# ncm2-path

> ncm2-path - Path Completion for Ncm2

This plugin contains 3 completion sources for ncm2:

1. `bufpath` - Path completions relative to current openning buffer

![ncm2-path-bufpath](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4538941/51010325-d4214400-158e-11e9-8d3b-a709527ee38d.png)

2. `cwdpath` - Path completions relative to current working directory

![ncm2-path-cwdpath](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4538941/51010326-d5eb0780-158e-11e9-8428-c0517d54e5b7.png)

3. `rootpath` - Path completions relative to root directory

![ncm2-path-rootpath](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4538941/51010334-d7b4cb00-158e-11e9-832c-17e19cced27a.png)

